snippet.title: Full Throttle II ZX Spectrum
snippet.description: Bog-standard sequel to an already bog-standard game.  Surely this could have done without one could it?  Sadly you STILL lose all of your speed with the softest kiss from another rider.  And the music gives me a headache!  Oh arses!
